{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"23":"Commercial Transactions (Kitab Al-Buyu)"},"section_detail":{"23":{"hadithnumber_first":3326,"hadithnumber_last":3415,"arabicnumber_first":3326,"arabicnumber_last":3415}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3375,"arabicnumber":3375,"text":"Câbir b. Abdillah (r.a)'dan rivayet edildiğine göre; Rasûlullah (s.a.v.), mu'âveme (seneliğine satış)'tan nehyetmiştir. Raviler (Saîd b. Mîna ve Ebû Zübeyr)'den birisi, (mu'âveme yerine) \"beyu's-sinîn\" dedi","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (1554)"}],"reference":{"book":23,"hadith":50}}]}